{"tid":103471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]司機酒駕撞兩車釀一死六傷","createTime":"2017-02-01T10:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T10:57:25.000Z","uid":32407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52205ceb55c12dc96880b1fad99287871b94c8dc","tid":103471,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/bkncn-20170201104602934-0201_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fbkncn-20170201104602934-0201_05011_001.html&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6675f71b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/bkncn-20170201104602934-0201_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170201/photo/bkncn-20170201104602934-0201_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170201%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170201104602934-0201_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=c3986e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江西宜豐市宜豐縣昨晚9時許發生嚴重交通意外，一輛白色私家車先與一輛車相撞，隨後再撞另一輛三輪車摩的（非法載客電單車)，釀成一死六傷。宜豐縣委宣傳部今日通報，指肇事司機涉嫌酒駕，現已被警方扣查。<br />\n<br />\n從網傳短片可見，事發後有多名傷者躺在地上等待救援，有救護員為傷者施行心肺復甦，很多途人在場圍觀。而涉事白色私家車車頭嚴重損毀，汽車零件散落一地。有目擊者稱，車禍發生時傳來巨響，當時還以為「有房屋倒塌」。<br />\n<br />\n恭喜發財 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}